beer.beer_description: Refreshing and flavoursome in style, STRUMAN’S Lager is brewed using only certified organic ingredients. Unfiltered, it has a bright amber colour with natural yeast cloud, and a crisp balanced taste derived from a combination of carefully sourced pilsner malt and noble hops (farm grown free from harsh chemicals). No preservatives or additives
